title: Don't Let People Label You
itunes:title: Don't Let People Label You
description:
People don’t determine your destiny; God does. If you’re going to rise to the next level you need to remove the negative labels that are holding you back.Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
